(108,	1,	'2025-04-09 09:05:05',	'2025-04-09 09:05:05',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tech4Youth is a not-for-profit organization dedicated to bridging the digital divide in underserved communities. Our mission is to empower youth with the skills, resources, and opportunities they need to succeed in today’s technology-driven world. Through our programs, workshops, and the Tech4Youth Learning Hub, we provide access to essential digital literacy, coding, and tech innovation training. We are committed to creating a more inclusive digital future, where every young person has the opportunity to thrive.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Mission</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To bridge the digital divide by providing young people in underserved communities with access to technology, training, and resources that will prepare them for a successful future in the digital age.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"className\":\"\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Vision</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"\"} -->\n<p>A world where every young person, regardless of their background, has the skills and opportunities to thrive in a tech-driven world.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"className\":\"\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Values</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Inclusion</strong>: Ensuring everyone has access to the digital tools and skills necessary for success.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Innovation</strong>: Encouraging creativity and problem-solving through technology.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Collaboration</strong>: Working together with communities, organizations, and tech professionals to make a greater impact.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><stro